{"tid":1726319,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"明報社評：中大學生會應與黑衣人割席","createTime":"2019-11-16T06:07:20.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T06:13:01.000Z","uid":5195,"like":1,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"a5b7e6bfb9faf860ca8228b5bdffb49b162b0389","tid":1726319,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:07:20.000Z","msg":"【明報社評】香港局勢急轉直下，大批身分不明的黑衣人進入多所大學，不斷囤積製造汽油彈等武器，又盜走大學實驗室內化學危險品。中大和理大校方表示，校園遭大規模破壞，緊急呼籲校內師生撤離，同時要求所有校外人馬上離開，中大校長段崇智更發出「求救」信號，稱倘若事態惡化，將尋求政府協助。校外黑衣人為了暴力鬥爭，不會事事以保護大學校園重要設施和學術瑰寶為念。中大校園告急，各方必須設法阻止最壞情况發生，學生組織應與校外黑衣人割席，請他們盡快離開，勿以校園作為「戰爭基地」，與校方合作一起恢復校園秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d519bf44d3cc925be44414dbd59d2ede91dfe4b6","tid":1726319,"uid":1425,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:08:01.000Z","msg":"割左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dislike.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />啦"},{"pid":"cfc0082b2727632cd8508124846f42db0d6719d5","tid":1726319,"uid":60434,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:08:42.000Z","msg":"又叫人割速龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbda2a781b18ea45232b8ed8cdb7bd1998adfb62","tid":1726319,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:10:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"759699600da40d4c9cde4c602468fb6bbccd6ad8","tid":1726319,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T06:13:01.000Z","msg":"明報社評墜落到同689同一水平<br />\n<br />\n中大學生會注意：689開到聲想你哋分化，做大台，公投，談判<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1722463\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1722463</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n雖然留意到信報都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.g